| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5920 — Recovery Inhibition (devman)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8cb258fc-07c1-5f35-a5dc-7a7a1e332765"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
